name: FCUPUXL : Akukira Motorku
description:
That night, when I was walking towards the parking lot. I saw motorbike that similar to mine. The color, the shape, the style, made me pretty sure it was mine. But not the stickers attached. It wasn't mine. It was someone else's.
That night, made me realize that I'm not the only one who has a motorbike like mine. 
So I walked.
